<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 19:59:01 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a36f102522a8</link><description>&lt;p&gt;罢工&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Part of a leaf hanging from a tree. It has been nibbled, and after the rain there are drops of water on it. The shape of the leaf, two larger drops and a hole in the leaf combine to form something that resembles a face with an open mouth and two large eyes. " height="1934" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a36f102522a8.jpg" width="1934"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 19:59:01 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a36b804bc9d4</link><description>&lt;p&gt;又可以在清单上添一项了。真有意思！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Weer eentje voor op ‘t lijstje. Curieus!" height="4012" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a36b804bc9d4.jpg" width="3004"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 15:55:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a366518bfe2e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;看向我们的前花园：一辆白色卡车停在篱笆后面。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="View into our frontgarden: a white truck is parked behind a fence. " height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/fihu/6a366518bfe2e.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://fihu.some.pics"&gt;@fihu&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 10:02:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>马德里更多塔楼</title><link>https://some.pics/6a36615bcfe99</link><description>&lt;p&gt;马德里更多塔楼&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="More towers in Md